<div id="event-{$id}" class="event contextmenuevent quickInfoEvent {if $eventtype==3}birthdays{/if}{if $updateAllowed} updateAlloweDd{/if}{if $calendarMode=='month'} monthevent {/if} enumColBGFade{$colors.id}"
	style="{if $calendarMode!='month'}top:{$top}px; left:{$left}px;{/if}
	{if $calendarMode=='week'} height:{$height}px;{/if}{if intval($width)>0} width:{$width}px;{/if}">
	<dl style="{if $calendarMode != 'month'}height:{$height}px;{/if}">
		<dt class="{if $calendarMode == 'month'}{else}enumColBG{$colors.id}{/if}">
			<span class="{if $calendarMode == 'month'}montheventTime{else}time{/if}">
				{$title}{if count($assignedUsers)==1} {$assignedUsers.0.shortname}{/if}
			</span>
		</dt>
		<dd><span class="{if $calendarMode=='week'}ca-elp{/if}" style="{if $calendarMode != 'month'}color:{$colors.text|default:"#000"};{/if}">

{* ---------- Only show title if event is not private ---------- *}
{if $is_private == 1}
	{if  $id_user == $current_user}
			<span class="privateEvent"></span>
			{if $is_repeated == 1}<span class="seriesEvent{if $calendarMode=='month'}Dark{/if}"></span>{/if}
			{$title}
	{else}
			<span class="privateEvent"></span>
		{if $is_repeated == 1}
			<span class="seriesEvent{if $calendarMode=='month'}Dark{/if}"></span>
		{/if}
	{/if}
{else}
		{if $is_repeated == 1}
			<span class="seriesEvent{if $calendarMode=='month'}Dark{/if}"></span>
		{/if}
			{$title}
{/if}
		</span></dd>
	</dl>
</div>